---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

// Live demo — WordPress Playground.
// Blueprint installs WP + Asteris theme + Pro Patterns plugin, activates dev mode
// (no licence needed inside sandbox per plugin's ASTERIS_PRO_PATTERNS_DEV constant).
// Lands at "Add New Page" so customer immediately hits the block inserter
// and can search/insert the 73 patterns.
const PLAYGROUND_URL = 'https://playground.wordpress.net/?blueprint-url=https://asteriscommerce.com/playground/pro-patterns-blueprint.json';
---
<Layout
  title="Try Asteris Pro Patterns — live in your browser, no purchase"
  description="A real WordPress install with the Asteris theme + Pro Patterns plugin active, running entirely in your browser via WordPress Playground. Browse and insert all 73 premium patterns before deciding whether to buy."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="eyebrow">★ LIVE IN YOUR BROWSER</div>
      <h1>Try Pro Patterns.<br /><span class="accent">All 73, before you buy.</span></h1>
      <p class="lead">
        A real WordPress install with <strong>the Asteris theme + Pro Patterns plugin</strong> active, running entirely in your browser. Open the block inserter, search for any pattern category — hero, e-commerce section, video, audio, page template — and insert it into a fresh page. No purchase, no licence key, no install.
      </p>
      <p class="boot">First boot takes ~30–60 seconds. The demo loads straight into a new page so the inserter is one click away.</p>
      <div class="hactions">
        <a href={PLAYGROUND_URL} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-pop btn-large">★ Launch the demo →</a>
        <a href="/asteris-pro-patterns/" class="btn-outline btn-large">Or read about Pro Patterns</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="status">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="sbox">
        <div class="seye">★ LIVE DEMO — ALL 73 PATTERNS ACTIVE, NO LICENCE NEEDED</div>
        <p>The Playground blueprint installs WordPress, the Asteris theme, and the Pro Patterns plugin in dev-mode (the licence check is bypassed inside the sandbox so you can browse every pattern). Want them in your own site? <a href="/asteris-pro-patterns/#buy">Buy a licence from $49/yr</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="active">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What to click first</h2>
      <p class="csub">Demo lands at <strong>Pages → Add New</strong> so the block inserter is one click away:</p>
      <div class="agrid">
        <div class="acol">
          <h3>Browse the patterns</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Click the <strong>+ (block inserter)</strong> top-left</li>
            <li>Switch to the <strong>Patterns</strong> tab</li>
            <li>Open the <strong>Asteris</strong> category in the sidebar</li>
            <li>Sub-categories: Hero · Shop · Composite · Video · Audio · Page templates</li>
            <li>Insert any pattern — it drops in as standard Gutenberg blocks</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="acol">
          <h3>Try a full page template</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Inserter → Asteris → <strong>Page templates</strong></li>
            <li>Pick <em>Webinar registration</em>, <em>Audiobook</em>, <em>Photographer</em>, <em>Coach</em>, etc.</li>
            <li>The whole layout drops in as one composition</li>
            <li>Edit any block — they're all standard core blocks underneath</li>
            <li>Hit <strong>Preview</strong> to see the front-end render</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="limits">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <h2>What works in Playground vs what doesn't</h2>
      <div class="lgrid">
        <div class="lcol works">
          <h3>★ Works</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>All 73 Pro Patterns in the inserter</li>
            <li>The Asteris theme (4 style variations + 14 product templates)</li>
            <li>Full Gutenberg editor — insert, edit, preview, publish</li>
            <li>Front-end render of any inserted pattern</li>
            <li>Site Editor + Styles panel for variations</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="lcol limited">
          <h3>★ Limited / unavailable</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>WooCommerce-specific patterns assume a real WC install (Shop patterns work, but no actual products)</li>
            <li>Video / Audio patterns use placeholder embeds in demo mode</li>
            <li>No persistent storage — close the tab and everything resets</li>
            <li>Licence key not required inside the sandbox (dev-mode)</li>
            <li>Want the theme without Pro Patterns? <a href="/try-theme/">Try the theme-only demo</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="after">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <h2>After the demo.</h2>
      <p>Pro Patterns is a licensed plugin — $49/yr founder for 1 site, locked-for-life. Add it to your own WordPress site via the standard plugin upload flow.</p>
      <div class="aactions">
        <a href="/asteris-pro-patterns/#buy" class="btn-pop btn-large">★ Buy Pro Patterns ($49/yr) →</a>
        <a href="/try-theme/" class="btn-outline btn-large">Or just try the free theme →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 36px; }
  .narrow { max-width: 820px; }

  .hero { padding: 80px 0 48px; }
  .hero .eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--c-violet);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(40px, 7vw, 80px); line-height: 0.98; letter-spacing: -2px; font-weight: 900; margin: 0 0 28px; }
  .hero h1 .accent { background: linear-gradient(transparent 55%, rgba(170, 0, 255, 0.20) 55%); padding: 0 4px; }
  .hero .lead { font-size: 20px; max-width: 760px; color: var(--c-text); line-height: 1.55; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .hero .lead strong { color: var(--c-text); font-weight: 700; }
  .hero .boot { font-size: 15px; color: var(--c-muted); margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .hactions { display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn-large { padding: 16px 28px; font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; border: 2px solid var(--c-black); border-radius: var(--r-md); text-decoration: none; }
  .btn-pop { background: var(--c-violet); color: #fff; border-color: var(--c-violet); }
  .btn-outline { background: transparent; color: var(--c-black); }
  .btn-pop:hover, .btn-outline:hover { transform: translate(-2px, -2px); box-shadow: var(--pop-shadow); }

  .status { padding: 32px 0; background: rgba(170, 0, 255, 0.08); }
  .sbox { background: var(--c-white); border: 2px solid var(--c-text); border-radius: 8px; padding: 22px 24px; }
  .seye { color: var(--c-violet); font-weight: 800; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .sbox p { font-size: 16px; color: var(--c-text); line-height: 1.55; margin: 0; }
  .sbox a { color: var(--c-violet); text-decoration: underline; font-weight: 600; }

  .active { padding: 80px 0; background: var(--c-white); border-top: 2px solid var(--c-text); border-bottom: 2px solid var(--c-text); }
  .active h2 { font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 42px); font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -1.5px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .csub { font-size: 17px; color: var(--c-muted); max-width: 760px; line-height: 1.55; margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .agrid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; }
  .acol h3 { font-size: 21px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 14px; color: var(--c-violet); }
  .acol ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  .acol li { padding: 6px 0 6px 22px; position: relative; font-size: 16px; color: var(--c-text); line-height: 1.5; }
  .acol li::before { content: '→'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--c-violet); font-weight: 700; }
  @media (max-width: 800px) { .agrid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .limits { padding: 80px 0; background: var(--c-bg); }
  .limits h2 { font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 36px); font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -1.2px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .lgrid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 18px; }
  .lcol { border: 2px solid var(--c-text); border-radius: 8px; padding: 22px; background: var(--c-white); }
  .works h3 { color: #1a7f37; font-size: 19px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .limited h3 { color: #c0392b; font-size: 19px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .lcol ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  .lcol li { padding: 6px 0 6px 22px; position: relative; font-size: 15px; color: var(--c-text); line-height: 1.55; }
  .works li::before { content: '✓'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #1a7f37; font-weight: 800; }
  .limited li::before { content: '⚠'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #c0392b; }
  .lcol a { color: var(--c-violet); text-decoration: underline; }
  @media (max-width: 800px) { .lgrid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .after { padding: 80px 0; background: var(--c-text); color: var(--c-white); text-align: center; border-top: 6px solid var(--c-violet); }
  .after h2 { font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 42px); font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -1.5px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #fff; }
  .after p { font-size: 18px; color: #ccc; max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto 24px; line-height: 1.6; }
  .aactions { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .after .btn-outline { background: var(--c-white); color: var(--c-text); border-color: var(--c-white); }
</style>
